Fruit juice 
Unique mixture of acrylic, nitro and spray paint. It’s one of 10 days everyday artwork. Fantastic feelings associated with nature in its colorful palette.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2018, spray paint on canvas, 90x90 cm, 2483x2470 pix.
